{"tid":1169991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例 = 和珅抄家","createTime":"2019-05-24T17:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T19:10:04.000Z","uid":7971,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e7f937ce1c5a05aa7d8cf161139f413de4ec0f","tid":1169991,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T17:25:40.000Z","msg":"清朝由康雍乾盛世 乾際十全武功 好大喜功<br />\n到 嘉慶 開始有衰落跡象 <br />\n第一個最明顯嘅事宜 就係抄第一貪官 和珅 <br />\n從而填補乾隆 好大喜功嘅洗費<br />\n<br />\n今日逃犯條例 一方面當然係咩國家安全乜乜柒柒<br />\n但其實更重要 係想抄班 大陸走資佬 <br />\n從而對抗 中美貿易 好似下圖咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/DoZ6PtrU4AA5Z5L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F10%2FDoZ6PtrU4AA5Z5L.jpg&h=ced6df92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/DoZ6PtjUwAAlQtu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F10%2FDoZ6PtjUwAAlQtu.jpg&h=ce42eb2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歷史永遠都係循環<br />\n中國人嘅劣根性 同 管治方式 根本唔會變<br />\n我更相信 中共步向清朝同一嘅道路"},{"pid":"801bd97768277f70fe445d5fa5ced0884efe5d7c","tid":1169991,"uid":59976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/biantailajiaomanhua/lj-05132019153120.html/190513RFA.jpg/@@images/17b40cc6-11d8-4a23-9985-816eb0f4aee5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fbiantailajiaomanhua%2Flj-05132019153120.html%2F190513RFA.jpg%2F%40%40images%2F17b40cc6-11d8-4a23-9985-816eb0f4aee5.jpeg&h=d5afe822&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27d7fc1d2a1335694749017cab8663b5487f1ceb","tid":1169991,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"和珅有料到架,佢雖然貪,但真係神通廣大"},{"pid":"cd8dab0592c47bfef0e6ffbd877f40cc99a1d4ce","tid":1169991,"uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27d7fc1d2a1335694749017cab8663b5487f1ceb","tid":1169991,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"和珅有料到架,佢雖然貪,但真係神通廣大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T19:10:04.000Z","msg":"其實依家個班走資派都係一樣"}]}